text: Hana Antunovic is a Swedish karateka. In 2018, she won one of the bronze medals in the women's kumite +68 kg event at the 2018 World Karate Championships held in Madrid, Spain. In 2015, she lost her bronze medal match in the women's kumite +68 kg event at the 2015 European Games held in Baku, Azerbaijan.
